Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:26.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:11.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:15.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:18.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(507.167,200.389)}Poison Gas Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(367.167620.389)}Torikabuto's Operation G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly an unusual plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The plant is making smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The plant is making smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone's car break down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I pity your fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but anyone who sees Shocker's latest\Nweapon, the killer plant, must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster killed someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru! You're incorrigible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, we gotta go to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's this coming from? You silly boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster... a monster killed someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not funny at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't scare me that easily, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But a monster really did kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't blame mama\Nif the monster kills you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The child saw it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The day of Operation: G draws near.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We will soon put our new weapon,\Nthe killer plant, to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, Torikabuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must silence the boy\Nwho witnessed our experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel, sir. I have a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The witness's name is Kimoto Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives in Machida, Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Torikabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence this Kimoto Mitsuru permanently!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The day Torikabuto silences that boy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is the day Operation: G goes into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen. Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will hereby explain the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just what was Colonel Zol's Operation: G?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:31.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plan revolved around their newly\Ndeveloped weapon, the killer plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:36.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They would set them around populous\Nvenues such as theaters and music halls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:42.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and use the gas the plants emit\Nto murder thousands of people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:46.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\c&H593CC7&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnChalk Stick}This monster killed someone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes five.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all of the same monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put one on this pole, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were behind this, Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you drawing this strange monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you taping them\Nto electric poles and mailboxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I really saw this monster kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a doctor look over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not! I'm not sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster really killed someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you, Mama! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru is the one drawing this monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says it killed someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:17.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Racing Club
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No use, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Incidents, incidents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two traffic accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's pretty boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of Shocker activity\Nfor the last twenty days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue skies in Tokyo and no sign of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel a little like I'm going soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling about, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shocker monster killed someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"This monster killed someone," it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a child's picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's very good.\NIt looks almost alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mitsuru's mom thinks\Nhe's sick or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Any mother would,\Nwho cares about her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But he says he saw it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro. Where is Mitsuru's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Hayato would believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Motomachi Block 17, Machida!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You really believe the boy's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think a child's mind could\Nconjure up a monster like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm borrowing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You FBI cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna tell Mr. Ichimonji the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what the doctor\Nsaid? You need rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:34.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an9\c&H593CC7&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnChalk Stick}This monster killed someone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lying about everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Mitsuru say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just... monsters\Nlike that don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mitsuru didn't say he was lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, is Mitsuru really sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the doctor couldn't\Nfind anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe\Nhe really saw a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My allies and I are fighting\Nhard against those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, let me speak to Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, you Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time fighting him.\NI'll be taking the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've arrived, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you have that child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll save Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"Poison gas plant"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, did you learn anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A plant that emits poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll analyze it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, contact me the\Nminute you learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's my fault that\NMitsuru was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:28.72,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider may have\Nlearned of our killer plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate Operation: G at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate Operation: G!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol. What about the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him alongside Goro\NIshikura and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Goro and his friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken measures\Nto deal with Goro and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You need only follow my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about the florist\Nthat sold us this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Mari and Yuri show up soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, why are you so\Nconcerned about the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster autograph\Nsession is starting at four!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster autograph session?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,Monster Autograph Session\NTicket
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready to head out, Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 30 minutes left! I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful! What a lovely flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the chairman\Nis finally thinking about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Mr. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Poison gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is experimenting with\Nplants that emit poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. Would you mind putting\Nin one more call to Mr. Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing. Just hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello, Pops?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato. Something's wrong at the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think something's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, hurry to the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:33.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Auto Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, open the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there! Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! They're not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting them to fresh\Nair should save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You made it out alive, Racing Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's too late to stop our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stage one of our plan will\Ncommence at four o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The children you count as your friends\Nwill die holding hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like the children they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He must mean Mitsuru, Goro, and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, we can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to save Mitsuru and Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But where do we start looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where Goro went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I knew there was\Nsomething off about that florist...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops! Do you know where Goro went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sky Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to some\Nmonster autograph session...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When's it scheduled for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Four o'clock, he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:16:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of monsters to be seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So many monsters!\NHurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters, monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here! Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get his autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get this one, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!\NLots of scary monsters right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They look familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.43,0:18:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cry, scream, suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can die with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one minute remains!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru... Th-They got you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kill us with\Nthat poison gas plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fifty seconds left...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty seconds remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill the children\Nright before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a fight you want, you've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro! Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a plant that makes poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! We can get out this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Where are you, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! He's about to spit that toxic fluid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rider!\N- Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru! Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mitsuru!\N- Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! Thank you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:25.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The battle had ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:28.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato, the Kamen Rider,\Nhad saved many young lives this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But he had no time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:34.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He had to always be ready,\Npreparing to fight new monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:37.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that could appear at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.58,Cont,,0,110,250,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)\fs70}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.52,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:45.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the lightning monster Eiking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:50.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker summons lightning to put the\NWorldwide Blackout Operation into motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but the Kamen Rider will\Nrise up to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:54.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:24:00.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "Lightning Monster Eiking's\NWorldwide Blackout Operation."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:24:00.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}Lightning Monster Eiking's\NWorldwide Blackout Operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:10.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:13.25,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:18.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:20.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:22.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.51,0:24:24.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.30,0:24:25.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.10,0:24:28.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.19,0:24:33.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.86,0:24:37.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.44,0:24:41.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.53,0:24:45.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison Gas Monster Torikabuto's Operation G